| Editor is non-interactive while panel is open | Fixed-position overlay sits above editor with pointer events capturing clicks (click-outside closes panel) |
| Named drafts pin to top of list | `getVersions` sort: named first (timestamp desc), then auto (timestamp desc) |
| Preview shows version content in read-only textarea | `VersionPreview` with `<textarea readOnly>` |
