5. **Sort modes**: Create 4 tasks with different severities. Switch sort to "Severity" — confirm critical appears first. Switch to "Quick wins" — confirm polish appears first. Switch to "Story order" — confirm task linked to lowest scene.order appears first; manuscript-level task appears last.

6. **Filter by severity**: Create tasks of different severities. Filter to "critical" only. Confirm only critical tasks show. Confirm "No tasks match this filter" state does not appear when there are critical tasks. Switch to a severity with no tasks; confirm empty filter state with "Clear filters" button.

7. **Filter by issue type and status**: Verify each filter select narrows the list correctly. Verify "Clear filters" button resets all three filter dropdowns to "all".

8. **Complete task**: Click "Done" on a task. Confirm its title gets strikethrough and the progress bar updates. Confirm it disappears from the "open" filtered view.

9. **Snooze task**: Click "Snooze" on a task. Confirm it moves toward the bottom of the list (after non-snoozed tasks), shows "Snoozed until {date 7 days from now}", and renders with reduced opacity. Switch filter to "open" — confirm snoozed task is not shown. Switch to "snoozed" filter — confirm it appears.

10. **Snooze expiry**: Open browser devtools. Use `localStorage` to edit the task's `snoozedUntil` to `Date.now() - 1`. Reload the page, navigate to Revision view. Confirm the task renders as `open` (no snoozed label, full opacity).

11. **Edit task**: Click "Edit" on a task. Confirm the form expands inline below the card with pre-filled values. Edit the title. Submit. Confirm the card updates immediately.

12. **Delete task**: Click "Delete" on a task. Confirm it's removed from the list and from localStorage. (No confirmation dialog in v1.)

13. **Progress bar**: Create 4 tasks: one each of critical/major/minor/polish. Mark critical and minor as done. Confirm progress bar shows "1/1" for critical, "0/1" for major, "1/1" for minor, "0/1" for polish. Confirm total summary reads "2 of 4 tasks done".

14. **Persistence**: Create tasks, reload the page, navigate back to Revision. Confirm tasks are still present.

15. **Accessibility keyboard nav**: Tab through the revision view. Confirm all four action buttons on each card are reachable. Confirm form fields have proper labels. Confirm sort/filter controls are keyboard operable.

16. **Responsive**: Resize browser to < 1024px. Confirm sidebar hides and main panel goes full-width. Resize to < 768px; confirm header wraps correctly.

