### Phase 2: Handoff lib (`src/lib/handoff.ts`)

localStorage keys (all per-story):
- `story-${storyId}-handoff-notes` → `HandoffNote[]`, capped at 10 (newest-first, prepend + slice)
- `story-${storyId}-session` → `SessionState`
- `handoff-recent-story` → `{ storyId: string; title: string; sessionUpdatedAt: string }` (latest story for home page)

sessionStorage key (tab-scoped snooze):
- `story-${storyId}-resume-dismissed` → `"true"`

Exported functions:
```ts
saveHandoffNote(storyId: string, note: Omit<HandoffNote, 'id' | 'createdAt'>): HandoffNote
getHandoffNotes(storyId: string): HandoffNote[]
getLatestHandoffNote(storyId: string): HandoffNote | null
saveSessionState(storyId: string, state: Omit<SessionState, 'updatedAt'>, storyTitle: string): void
