1. Four mode buttons visible (Editor/Corkboard/Submissions/Timeline) with correct `aria-pressed`
2. Click Timeline → layout renders without console errors
3. Scenes with `timelineDate` set out-of-order → Timeline sorts them chronologically
4. Scenes without `timelineDate` → appear after dated scenes; show "No date" badge + dashed left border
5. Click marker chip → inline input appears with autoFocus; Enter saves; Escape cancels without saving
6. Same for storyline tag chip
