## Observability

All existing `console.log` patterns in the codebase are retained. Add the following in the lib layer:

- `createEntity`: `console.log('Created entity:', entity.id, entity.type, entity.name)`
- `updateEntity`: `console.log('Updated entity:', entityId, updates)`
- `deleteEntity`: `console.log('Deleted entity:', entityId, 'and its links')`
- `linkEntityToScene`: `console.log('Linked entity', entityId, 'to scene', sceneId)`
- `unlinkEntityFromScene`: `console.log('Unlinked entity', entityId, 'from scene', sceneId)`

These match the verbosity of `scenes.ts` and `stories.ts` and aid debugging in browser devtools.

